public static class CalculatorParser3.CalcNode extends imagingbook.parboiled.trees.ImmutableBinaryTreeNode<CalculatorParser3.CalcNode>
The AST node for the calculators. The type of the node is carried as a Character that can either contain an operator char or be null. In the latter case the AST node is a leaf directly containing a value.
